Recording Features:
------------------
- Automatic recording starts when call connects to bot
- Records both sides of conversation (caller + bot)
- Organized by date folders (auto-created daily)
- Unique filenames prevent overwrites
- WAV format for universal compatibility
- Option 'b' means recording only during bridged call

To Access Recordings:
--------------------
# List recordings from container
docker exec ava-asterisk ls -la /var/spool/asterisk/monitor/

# Copy recording to local system
docker cp ava-asterisk:/var/spool/asterisk/monitor/2025-11-09/recording.wav ./

# Play recording locally
paplay recording.wav

